c: 17
v: 60
t: "Futhi ngenkathi sithi kuwena, “ngempela iNkosi yakho ibazungelezile abantu futhi asizange siwenze umbono esakubonisa wona ngaphandle kokuba ube isivivinyo kubantu nesihlahla esiqalekisiweyo kwi-Qur’an, futhi siyabaxwayisa ukuthi ayikho into eyonezelela kubona ngaphandle kokuduka okukhulu”"